{"title":"白杨","authors":["张新泉"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":3,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"白杨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张新泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片小手，翠绿地摇着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在火焰山下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个多毛驴多葡萄架的小镇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像是等待了许多年许多年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——小白杨的仪仗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已长成林带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坎儿井不再蒸腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撩人的土腥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待了许多年许多年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小手们终于举向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个最潇洒的角度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里，那里，朝我们的汽车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇响绿叶般的纯情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一种舞蹈，一种心歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在土路两侧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在矮墙后面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着驴蹄嗒嗒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手鼓声声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手有些儿脏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但并不过份"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和那些脏兮兮的小眼睛小鼻子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成戈壁滩上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最迷人的风景……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小手在拔节、生长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把无边的漠野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩绘成一方荧屏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大荒凉大寂寞的背景上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也忘情地升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的手掌；我的每一滴泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在应答——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！未来；啊！知音"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}